reviewText: This is not your average Miss Marple. Margaret Rutledge is a spry older woman who doesn't let the moss grow under her feet and solves crimes with every ounce of her body and will literally tackle a killer to bring them down. The stories are fantastic. Great cast in all the stories.
It does not work on USA dvd players.
Very retro. Very fun. Good for people who like old-fashioned stuff.
